Problems with Constants, Low Severity (94)

Ecore.h
[+] ECORE_EVENT_COUNT
Change Effect
1 The value of constant ECORE_EVENT_COUNT has been changed from 6 to 11. Applications will pass an old value of this constant as the parameter to the new-version library functions, that expect a new one. This may result in crash of incorrect behavior of applications.
